FBIS4-31348 "dreeu110__a94029" FBIS-EEU-94-110-A Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 ANNEX Yugoslavia, Kosovo Police Arrest 3 Pristina University Officials Police Arrest 3 Pristina University Officials AU0406141294 Tirana ATA in English 1024 GMT 3 Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0406141294 Tirana ATA English BFN [Text] Tirana, June 3 (ATA) -- Fadil Berisha, chairman of the assembly of the Pristina university, Destan Halimi, secretary, and Sali Maqesonci, of the rectorate, have been put under arrest for two days now. The Serb police interrupted the proceedings of the assembly of the Pristina University on May 31, and besides the above three persons, it also arrested Prof. Dr. Ejup Statovci, rector of the university, Selman Brymen and other leading officials, who were released later, according to the information centre of Kosova.
